section.better
  .container
    .row
      .col-xl-12.text-xs-center
        h2.text-uppercase.m-t-0 You deserve a 
          .titile-better better 
          |  way to raise the money you need to grow.
        h3.font-weight-light.m-t-0 Our technology stack was built to maximize your exposure and minimize your costs.
    .row
      .col-xl-4.better-item
        .photo
          img(src=require('images/list-1.png'), alt="")
        h4.title.text-uppercase List Your Fundraise
        .text
          p We want you to focus on what you do best: build your company. We’ll help you assess your valuation, prepare your offering docs and handle filings and all the heavy lifting.
      .col-xl-4.better-item
        .photo
          img(src=require('images/network1.png'), alt="")
        h4.title.text-uppercase Activate Your Network
        .text
          p Think of our platform as a way to raise 150% or more of the money you can raise from your own network. Get your customer, community, friends and family to invest early and often. Once you create the momentum, our investor network can provide meaningful additional capital. 
      .col-xl-4.better-item
        .photo
          img(src=require('images/invest-list.png'), alt="")
        h4.title.text-uppercase Everybody can Invest!
        .text
          p BRAND NEW! Everybody in the world can now invest in America’s entrepreneurs. Capture their interest with your story and use your network to get early traction – and our massive network will surely follow!
    .row
      .col-xl-8.offset-xl-2.bottom-wrap
        .row
          .col-xl-6
            .item
              i.fa.fa-chevron-right
              h3.font-weight-light Time to raise money on
